### Manifest guardrails

- Keep `manifest.permissions` minimal; only add what the feature truly needs.
- Restrict `host_permissions` to exact origins and paths when possible.
- Update `default_locale` messages in [public/\_locales/en/messages.json](mdc:public/_locales/en/messages.json) (and other locales) when UI strings change.
- See current manifest and mappings in [wxt.config.ts](mdc:wxt.config.ts).

### When changing permissions or routes

- Document the reason in the PR description.
- Verify UI copy is localized in `public/_locales/*`.
- Rebuild and test on all targeted browsers when using `pnpm build:all`.

### Path aliases

Preferred aliases defined here:

- `@components` → `components/`
- `@lib` → `lib/`
- `@assets` → `assets/`
- `@entry` → `entrypoints/`

Prefer absolute imports using these aliases across the codebase.

### Icons & packaging

- Icons: `public/icons/*` for bundled assets.
- Zip artifact naming is controlled here; keep consistent before releases.
